            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "```suggestion\n• |vim.lsp.buf.declaration()|, |vim.lsp.buf.definition()|, |vim.lsp.buf.definition()|,\n  and |vim.lsp.buf.implementation()| no longer accept the `reuse_win` option.\n  Use 'switchbuf' to control this behavior instead.\n```",
            "commit_id": "290238dcdaddd3d09ab014bb9e4cd21cb1faa775",
            "created_at": "2026-03-29T23:56:55Z",
